modemu2k (0.2.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * debian/control: bump debhelper-compat to 13; add meson, ninja-build,
    pkg-config, doxygen, and groff to Build-Depends; drop flex
    (cmdlex.c is shipped pre-generated); drop the stale Devuan Vcs-Git
    line; rewrite Description; bump Standards-Version to 4.6.2; add
    Rules-Requires-Root: no.
  * debian/rules: switch to dh --buildsystem=meson with hardening=+all
    and -Dgen-docs=true / -Dhelper-scripts=true so the HTML API docs
    and m2k-{minicom,picocom} wrappers ship in the package.
  * debian/compat: dropped (replaced by debhelper-compat in control).
  * debian/copyright: sync to GPL-2-or-later (matches the source
    headers and the upstream COPYING).

 -- Andy Alt <arch_stanton5995@proton.me>  Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000

